A brow grooming and shaping kit that will help you create a perfect set of arches.
Brow Fix Brow Kit Light includes:2 Brow Powders 1 Hi-Lite Powder 1 Mini Tweezer 1 Mini Brow Brush 1 Mini Sponge Applicator
Be your own brow guru, shaping your brows is as easy as 1-2-3!
Made in USA
Product Ingredients:Hi-Lite Ingredients:  Talc, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Zinc Stearate, Dimethicone, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Coco-Caprylate/Caprate, Phenoxyethanol, Polyethylene, Sodium Dehydroacetate, Sorbic Acid, May Contain (+/-):  Mica (CI 77019), Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Bismuth Oxychloride (CI 77163).
Brow 1 Ingredients:  Talc, Boron Nitride, Silica, Nylon-12, Zea Mays (Corn) Starch, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Zinc Stearate, Dimethicone, Phenoxyethanol, Sodium Dehydroacetate, Sorbic Acid, May Contain (+/-):  Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499).
Brow 2 Ingredients:  Talc, Boron Nitride, Silica, Nylon-12, Zea Mays (Corn) Starch, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Zinc Stearate, Dimethicone, Sodium Dehydroacetate, Phenoxyethanol, Sorbic Acid, May Contain (+/-):  Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Chromium Hydroxide Green (CI 77289), Chromium Oxide Greens (CI 77288).Tweeze excess hairs from brows. Make sure to tweeze in direction of hair growth.Apply hi-lite powder to brow bone with sponge brush applicator to define arch.Blend and apply brow powder colors to fill & shape perfect looking brows.
